trans-unit.source: Represents data that is sent with a <xref href="System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D.Started"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje dane są przesyłane z <xref href="System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D.Started"> </xref> zdarzeń.

trans-unit.source: Gets the x-coordinate of the origin.

The origin point represented by the OriginX and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DStartedEventArgs.OriginY%2A> properties is the average position of all manipulators associated with an element.
trans-unit.target: Punktem początkowym reprezentowany przez OriginX i <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DStartedEventArgs.OriginY%2A>Właściwości to średnia pozycja manipulatory wszystkie skojarzone z elementem.</xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DStartedEventArgs.OriginY%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the y-coordinate of the origin.

The origin point represented by the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DStartedEventArgs.OriginX%2A> and OriginY properties is the average position of all manipulators associated with an element.
trans-unit.target: Punktem początkowym reprezentowany przez <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DStartedEventArgs.OriginX%2A>i OriginY właściwości to średnia pozycja manipulatory wszystkie skojarzone z elementem.</xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.Manipulation2DStartedEventArgs.OriginX%2A>
